<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>95</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 xiōng huái shì jiè xiōng huái yǔ zhòu fēi yuè de shí dài zǒu chū wǒ men de jiǎo bù
 tóu dǐng yī fāng tiān jiǎo tà shuǐ hé tǔ wǒ men bù shì liú làng hàn yě bù shì nuò fū
 yé hé huá de jūn duì tóu zhì áng yáng yé hé huá de jūn duì yǒng gǎn xiàng qián zǒu
 yào bǎ fú yīn de huǒ bǎ dì gěi nà biān de rén wǒ men tuán jié yī zhì gāo shān yě ràng lù
 shuō shén me nán shuō shén me kǔ yīn nà biān shì yī gè gèng měi de guó dù</lyrics>
<title>xiōng huái shì jiè 迦南95</title>
</song>